==WYSIWYM editors== [[WYSIWYM]] (what you see is what you mean) is an alternative paradigm to WYSIWYG, in which the focus is on the semantic structure of the document rather than on the presentation. These editors produce more logically structured markup than is typical of [[WYSIWYG]] editors, while retaining the advantage in ease of use over hand-coding using a text editor. * [[Lyx]] * [[WYMeditor]]
