'''''Redemption: The Myth of Pet Overpopulation and the No Kill Revolution in America''''' is a book by author [[Nathan Winograd]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/animalia/wp/2017/01/23/whats-a-no-kill-animal-shelter-the-answer-is-more-complicated-than-it-seems/|title=What’s a ‘no-kill’ animal shelter? The answer is more complicated than it seems.|newspaper=[[The Washington Post]]|accessdate=10 August 2018}}</ref>
